snippet.title: AMBER'S DONE - Jason Momoa FURIOUSLY Reacts To Amber NOT Being Fired for Aquaman 2 | Celebrity Craze
snippet.description:
AMBER'S DONE - Jason Momoa FURIOUSLY Reacts To Amber NOT Being Fired for Aquaman 2 | Celebrity Craze

Did Amber Heard just get booted for Aquaman 2? This would be great news to Johnny Depp and Aquaman fans around the world. The #FireAmberHeard movement is going strong. It seems the Aquaman 2 director, James Wan, does not even want Amber Heard in the movie. 

It seems like everyone is turning against Amber Heard. The Johnny Depp Amber Heard legal battle is still at the forefront of celebrity news.

Elon Musk, Jason Momoa, Angelina Jolie, Joe Rogan, and others have all WHO DEFENDED Johnny Depp with PROOF from Amber Heard.

While some celebrities prefer living a quiet life away from the public, others just have so many scandals following them. In this video, we are going to talk about Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, who have been on each other’s throats ever since they split up and how Amber Heard might be facing jail time for one mistake she made in all this.

With the initial court date being pushed back, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been given some more time in order to gather more evidence for their individual cases. For quite some time, the two were firing evidence at each other in order to win in court. 

Ever since the recent release of the footage of the LAPD officers from the penthouse night of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, things have not been looking all too bright for Amber Heard. Her team has been working tirelessly in order to back up her side, however Johnny Depp seems to have made the attempt to strike back.

Now it turns out that Amber Heard may have not written the statement or OP ED in accusations against Johnny Depp. This could another case of defamation or fraud. Let's break it down in today's video.

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnnyDepp #AmberHeardJail​ #AmberHeardCourt​ #JusticeForJohnny
